milestones.description: Hadlee has taken the most five-wicket hauls (2) in ODIs for NZ, going past Chatfield's record
Hadlee has become the top wicket-taker for NZ in ODIs with 34 wickets, going past Lance Cairns's 31
Greg Chappell and Allan Border's 65-run partnership is AUS's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 60 between Greg Chappell and Ross Edwards
